      <title>拜登退出大选后，民主党时间不多了，修改了党代会</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/08/16/nx-s1-5052067/with-not-a-lot-of-time-democrats-revamp-convention-after-biden-pulls-out-of-election</link>
